{
  "stem": "24125.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Since it was fall, I managed to lie down very flat and cover myself with leaves and lived through till they passed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When they passed, I continued to go to my mother and joined them there for a very short while.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The person that I told you, that Russian, [INAUDIBLE], they tortured him because they thought that he knows where I am.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they hanged him because of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So that was the end-- that I decide that this is the time that I should part.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When I said, mother and father-- forgive me, it's only mother because father was not alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I went, straight-- packed myself, and went straight to a family, Ukrainian, that lived near Kiev, not far away from Kiev.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I knew one of their members.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She lived in Stadniki and worked in Stadniki.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was accepted there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was staying there till they had enough food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After they had no food, there was no place for me to stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing I felt-- to go back to other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then, I was worried because my looks were Semitic looks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that the language didn't help too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I heard them talking about partisans, that our partisans are forming, that they accepting members.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They want all the young man to join them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when came to female, it was hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't-- they didn't-- they were not willing to accept too many females.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But obviously, since it was my life and death, I tried to meet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I did meet one of the partisans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I met him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He right away, fell in love with me, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
